folder: Benson Avenue & Bay 35th Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Benson Avenue, south side, from Bay 35th Street to 24th Avenue, viewing west from the latter and showing Public School No. 101. An addition to the school was later built behind this building.

Board of Education of the City of New York

December 21, 1927
